      "comment_id" : 138413596,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Ok, you might want to add option <code>-S</code> to env command.  <code>#!&#47;bin&#47;bin&#47;env -S java --source 11</code>.  See the manual page for <code>env</code> for the reason."
